name: __ENiagaraScalabilityUpdateFrequency
doc: Controls how often should we update scalability states for these effects.

SpawnOnly: Scalability will be checked only on spawn.
Low: Scalability will be checked every 1.0s (default for fx.NiagaraScalabilityUpdateTime_Low).
Medium: Scalability will be checked every 0.5s (default for fx.NiagaraScalabilityUpdateTime_Medium).
High: Scalability will be checked every 0.25s (default for fx.NiagaraScalabilityUpdateTime_High).
Continuous: Scalability will be checked every frame.
